{"tid":2077186,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"證監：正與兩地監管及交易所合作 為推交易所債券通","createTime":"2020-06-24T05:55:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T05:55:28.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8476a59adb5b2635047226322033269d770b78b5","tid":2077186,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T05:55:28.000Z","msg":"證監：正與兩地監管及交易所合作 為推交易所債券通<br />\n2020-06-24 HKT 13:20<br />\n<br />\n香港證監會主席雷添良及行政總裁歐達禮表示，香港將繼續保持作為門戶的優勢，連接內地與海外的資金流，繼2014年開通股票市場交易互聯互通機制後，將著手引入其他互聯互通項目，並會首先推出有關跨境買賣上市債券的新措施。<br />\n<br />\n證監會指，現正與中國證監會及兩地交易所合作，為於香港及內地交易所上市或買賣的合資格債券，推出交易所債券通(Exchange Bond Connect)機制。<br />\n<br />\n(已節錄)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533844-20200624.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533844-20200624.htm&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPq2paxXJRTFpYESBXKIXFX0%3D&h=03e465d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533844-20200624.htm&h=1ed9d2ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533844-20200624.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>繼滬港通及深港通之後的另一份大禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"}]}